</p>

<h2>The Bottom Line</h2>

<p>
  Between is the veteran messenger for couples who basically want a private chat with a shared timeline — and its lifetime price is genuinely good. OurCouple is for couples who want their whole relationship — rituals, memories, plans and play — in one private, encrypted space, with a single subscription for both. Both are solid; pick by how you actually want to spend time together.
</p>

